<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Harvest_Gypsies:_On_the_Road_to_the_Grapes_of_Wrath&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Harvest Gypsies: On the Road to the Grapes of Wrath (page does not exist)">The Harvest Gypsies: On the Road to the Grapes of Wrath</a></i> (1936)</li>
