<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Grapes_of_Wrath" title="The Grapes of Wrath">The Grapes of Wrath</a></i> (1939)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Forgotten_Village&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Forgotten Village (page does not exist)">Forgotten Village</a></i> (1941)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Log_from_the_Sea_of_Cortez" title="The Log from the Sea of Cortez">Sea of Cortez: A Leisurely Journal of Travel and Research</a></i> (1941)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Moon_Is_Down" title="The Moon Is Down">The Moon Is Down</a></i> (1942)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Bombs_Away:_The_Story_of_a_Bomber_Team" title="Bombs Away: The Story of a Bomber Team">Bombs Away: The Story of a Bomber Team</a></i> (1942)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Cannery_Row_(novel)" title="Cannery Row (novel)">Cannery Row</a></i> (1945)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Wayward_Bus" title="The Wayward Bus">The Wayward Bus</a></i> (1947)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Pearl_(novel)" title="The Pearl (novel)">The Pearl</a></i> (1947)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/A_Russian_Journal" title="A Russian Journal">A Russian Journal</a></i> (1948)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Burning_Bright" title="Burning Bright">Burning Bright</a></i> (1950)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Log_from_the_Sea_of_Cortez" title="The Log from the Sea of Cortez">The Log from the Sea of Cortez</a></i> (1951)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/East_of_Eden" title="East of Eden">East of Eden</a></i> (1952)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Sweet_Thursday" title="Sweet Thursday">Sweet Thursday</a></i> (1954)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Short_Reign_of_Pippin_IV" title="The Short Reign of Pippin IV">The Short Reign of Pippin IV: A Fabrication</a></i> (1957)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Once_There_Was_A_War" title="Once There Was A War" class="mw-redirect">Once There Was A War</a></i> (1958)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Winter_of_Our_Discontent" title="The Winter of Our Discontent">The Winter of Our Discontent</a></i> (1961)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Travels_with_Charley:_In_Search_of_America" title="Travels with Charley: In Search of America">Travels with Charley: In Search of America</a></i> (1962)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/America_and_Americans" title="America and Americans">America and Americans</a></i> (1966)</li>
</ul>
<p>Posthumous:</p>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Journal_of_a_Novel:_The_East_of_Eden_Letters" title="Journal of a Novel: The East of Eden Letters">Journal of a Novel: The East of Eden Letters</a></i> (1969)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Viva_Zapata!" title="Viva Zapata!">Viva Zapata!</a></i> (1975)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Acts_of_King_Arthur_and_His_Noble_Knights" title="The Acts of King Arthur and His Noble Knights">The Acts of King Arthur and His Noble Knights</a></i> (1976)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Workings_Days:_The_Journals_of_The_Grapes_of_Wrath&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Workings Days: The Journals of The Grapes of Wrath (page does not exist)">Workings Days: The Journals of The Grapes of Wrath</a></i> (1989)</li>
</ul>
